---
const siteUrl = 'https://hauslybr.com';
const title = 'Hausly CRM | CRM para corretores';
const description =
  'Hausly CRM organiza leads, visitas e carteira em um fluxo simples para corretores venderem mais no Brasil, com foco inicial em Goias e Goiania.';
---

<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="robots" content="index,follow" />
    <link rel="canonical" href={siteUrl} />

    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Hausly CRM" />
    <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:url" content={siteUrl} />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={title} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={description} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="page">
      <section class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">CRM para Corretores</p>
        <h1>Transforme leads em fechamentos sem planilhas e sem caos</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          O Hausly CRM centraliza funil, visitas, carteira de imoveis e
          acompanhamento de proxima acao em um fluxo claro para o mercado
          brasileiro.
        </p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:contato@hauslybr.com"
            >Falar com o time</a
          >
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://api.hauslybr.com/docs"
            >Ver API Docs</a
          >
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Funil objetivo</h2>
          <p>
            Acompanhe cada lead por etapa, sem perder timing de follow-up e com
            visao clara das proximas acoes.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Visitas organizadas</h2>
          <p>
            Agenda integrada e historico por lead para reduzir no-show e acelerar
            decisoes, com rotina aderente ao dia a dia do corretor.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Foco Brasil, base Goias</h2>
          <p>
            Estrategia nacional, validacao inicial em Goiania e Goias para
            evoluir produto com dados reais de operacao.
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    color-scheme: light;
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family:
      "Avenir Next",
      "Segoe UI",
      sans-serif;
    color: #0f172a;
    background:
      radial-gradient(1200px circle at 10% 10%, #dbeafe 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(900px circle at 90% 15%, #fde68a 0%, transparent 45%),
      #f8fafc;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 72px 24px;
  }

  .hero {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #1d4ed8;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.08;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .subtitle {
    margin: 20px 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #334155;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #0f172a;
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgb(15 23 42 / 20%);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: #fff;
    border-color: #cbd5e1;
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .grid {
    margin-top: 56px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 16px;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .card {
    background: rgb(255 255 255 / 84%);
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 20px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #334155;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .page {
      padding: 56px 18px;
    }
  }
</style>
